{"tid":2142542,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「反制」英國的上上策 - 古德明","createTime":"2020-08-06T13:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T13:20:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5e0b55da30602ccef556e611c70222a104eb03e7","tid":2142542,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:01:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200719/2JPIVSAGFNFK3LL73YW7DBL26A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200719%2F2JPIVSAGFNFK3LL73YW7DBL26A%2F&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOjC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=743024b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200719%2F2JPIVSAGFNFK3LL73YW7DBL26A%2F&h=83a38bb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200719/2JPIVSAGFNFK3LL73YW7DBL26A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n「反制」英國的上上策 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dxobTP-U-azFY21oj4RLJPGqHvQ=/1920x1440/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/72ZPWFJ4HBFEPM7LS7TA45N3OY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdxobTP-U-azFY21oj4RLJPGqHvQ%3D%2F1920x1440%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F72ZPWFJ4HBFEPM7LS7TA45N3OY.jpg&h=1edcd215&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共無視《中英聯合聲明》，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n七月二十三日。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中共可以做的其實很多。去年，美國向入口的新中國貨品加徵關稅，中共也就向入口的美國貨品加徵關稅；最近，美國制裁中共治疆高官，關閉中共駐侯斯頓總領事館，中共也就制裁美國國會議員，關閉美國駐成都總領事館。現在，英國容許港人赴英定居，中共也可照樣宣布：「英國人可到中國定居，居住滿五年，即可獲永久居留權；再居住一年，即可獲中國國籍。」這樣，英國人一定奔走相告，絡繹來歸，大長中共威風，大滅歐美帝國主義者志氣。<br />\n<br />\n中共外交部說「英國違反承諾在先」，完全不提承諾載於什麼文件，非常高明。香港鄭月娥政府低手得多，竟然指摘「英國違反《中英聯合聲明》附件中的承諾」，忘了中共早已多次宣布「《中英聯合聲明》已完成其歷史任務，只是一分歷史文件」。鄭月娥有空，應多學習習近平外交思想。"},{"pid":"60393582c1f4fe4175f702e1877aee7fe7ed8a0b","tid":2142542,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:04:58.000Z","msg":"【飛雲】影一張相等於7000蚊嘅時代來臨了！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2142541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2142541</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aeb2c0a995f6cfb1b135e9519023e6e0c02cac8b","tid":2142542,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}